    <h4>Maps: </h4>
    <p align="justify"><a href="http://www.uci.edu/campusmap/">Campus maps </a> are available. We strongly encourage you to print one and bring it with you. The directions below guide you to a parking lot. The map will help you navigate the campus once you park. </p>
    <h4>Parking Permits: </h4>
    <p align="justify">Permits are required at UCI. Please visit the <a href="http://www.parking.uci.edu/">UCI Parking website </a> for information on obtaining a permit. </p>
    <h4>Directions: </h4>
    <p align="justify">The CERT project is housed on the 4th floor of the Calit2 Building at UCI. </p>
    <p align="justify"><span style="font-weight: bold">From 73 South</span>: exit at Bison Ave. Turn LEFT. Make a RIGHT on E. Peltason Dr. Take the first LEFT hand turn into parking lot 12B. If you make it to the stop sign you have gone too far. </p>
    <p align="justify"><span style="font-weight: bold">From 73 North</span>: exit at Bison Ave. Turn RIGHT. Make a RIGHT on E. Peltason Dr. Take the first LEFT hand turn into parking lot 12B. If you make it to the stop sign you have gone too far. </p>
    <p align="justify"><span style="font-weight: bold">From 5/405 South</span> : take 55 South to the 73 south. exit at Bison Ave. Turn LEFT. Make a RIGHT on E. Peltason Dr. Take the first LEFT hand turn into parking lot 12B. If you make it to the stop sign you have gone too far. <br />
        <br />
        <span style="font-weight: bold">From 5/405 North</span>: exit at Jeffrey/University, turning left (Jeffrey turns to University at the 405). Go to Culver Ave. and turn LEFT. Go to Campus Ave. and turn RIGHT. Go to E. Peltason Dr. and turn LEFT. You will pass 2 stop signs. After the 2nd stop sign, turn RIGHT into lot 12B. If you get to Bison Ave, you have gone too far. </p>
